snippet.title: Sasta Biig Bosss 2 | Parody | Ashish Chanchlani
snippet.description:
Acv presents the second season of ‚ÄúSASTA BIIG BOSSS‚Äù
Chalo pehle brand waalo ka description daalte because PAISAAAA 

WOW Skin Science: ACV Shampoo & Face Wash

Amazon: https://amzn.to/3Xs8zo1 
Flipkart: https://bit.ly/3K06s7I
Nykaa: http://bit.ly/3HVUQ2W

BuyWow: http://bit.ly/3XnDn9y
(Use ASHISHWOW20 for an extra 20% discount)

Haan haan maalum
Hai hume bahut late ho gaya aane mein
Pure 10 nahi nahi 11 mahine lag gaye hume
Lekin tum log ko kya batau aisi fatti padi thi hum log ka kuch aisa project tha jisse plan karte karte karte 6-7 mahine aise nikle hume pata hi nai chala
Fir humne ye saal ka bigg boss dekha aur decide kiya abhi toh hum season 2 banaenge hi kaise bhi
Wo jo project hai jiski baat kar raha hu abhi back burner pe hai but promise hai hum usse kaise bhi aapke saamne laaengeüòç

Abhi subah ke 6 baje main ye description bathroom mein likh raha hu seth log toh please deri ke lie maaf kar do baaki tum log hi seth ho mere dhani ho muje maalum hai naraazgi hogi lekin utna hi pyaar bhi karte ho
Chalo abhi video ka Favourite part comment karo aur apna fav dialogue bhi likh lo

Chalo abhi production ka batao is video ka

Actors : wahi sasti team jisme dusre actors ki kami hoti, Akash Dodeja aka jadoo aka gareeb Kunal Chhabhria aka is baar wo kisi ke baap nahi gaya Vibhu Varshney humare video ke super star Simran Dhanwani rotlu pitbul Rohit Sadhwani belt waala anti-singham Tanish Sirwani sandaswala Grishim Nawani dubai waala Akash Jagtap thapad khaane waala Paras rupani playground ka rejected player, Ritesh Sadhwani bhi tha video mein bas ek scene mein kyunki saala gumm ho gaya tha Shivkumar Parthasarathy as humare big-bull Vivek Menon humare super super star as humare host
And ajay bhai jinhone teddy bear ka body double play kiya 

Writer & Director : main hi hu saalo
Editor : wo bhi main hi hu saalo
Background music - Vivek-Abhishek (inka channel dekho bahut talented hai mere bhai log : https://youtube.com/c/VIVEKABHISHEK)
Production Head: Jashan Sirwani & Tanish Sirwani (saara paisa ye log khaa jaate rent aur camera kaüò°)
DOP : Ujjawal Gayakwad,Sidharth Kedare
Assistant DOP : Hemendra Singh, Yogi
Gaffer : Ramchandra Vishwakarma
Sound : Satya Narayan
Lights : Golden Lights 
Location : Mania Location
Art : Ravi Kondke and Team
Makeup : Akbar Ali Shaikh and Team
Production : Tushar Manejar and Team

#SastaBiigBosss2 #AshishChanchlani #Acv

snippet.description:
What if love was only a text away?üíïüì± #LoveAgainMovie, featuring new music by @CelineDion, starring @priyankachopra and Sam Heughan is exclusively in movie theaters Mother‚Äôs Day.

What if a random text message led to the love of your life? In this romantic comedy, dealing with the loss of her fianc√©, Mira Ray sends a series of romantic texts to his old cell phone number‚Ä¶ not realizing the number was reassigned to Rob Burns‚Äô new work phone. A journalist, Rob is captivated by the honesty in the beautifully confessional texts. When he‚Äôs assigned to write a profile of megastar Celine Dion (playing herself in her first film role), he enlists her help in figuring out how to meet Mira in person‚Ä¶and win her heart. Starring Priyanka Chopra Jonas, Sam Heughan and Celine Dion and featuring multiple new songs from Dion, Love Again, written for the screen and directed by Jim Strouse, is only in theaters May 12, 2023.

‚ûΩ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
‚ûΩ Snapchat - @dream

snippet.title: The Flash ‚Äì Official Trailer
snippet.description:
On June 16, worlds collide. Watch the official trailer now for The Flash ‚Äì only in theaters. #TheFlashMovie 

Warner Bros. Pictures presents ‚ÄúThe Flash,‚Äù directed by Andy Muschietti (the ‚ÄúIT‚Äù films, ‚ÄúMama‚Äù). Ezra Miller reprises their role as Barry Allen in the DC Super Hero‚Äôs first-ever standalone feature film.

Worlds collide in ‚ÄúThe Flash‚Äù when Barry uses his superpowers to travel back in time in order to change the events of the past. But when his attempt to save his family inadvertently alters the future, Barry becomes trapped in a reality in which General Zod has returned, threatening annihilation, and there are no Super Heroes to turn to. That is, unless Barry can coax a very different Batman out of retirement and rescue an imprisoned Kryptonian‚Ä¶ albeit not the one he‚Äôs looking for. Ultimately, to save the world that he is in and return to the future that he knows, Barry‚Äôs only hope is to race for his life. But will making the ultimate sacrifice be enough to reset the universe? 

‚ÄúThe Flash‚Äù ensemble also includes rising star Sasha Calle, Michael Shannon (‚ÄúBullet Train,‚Äù ‚ÄúBatman v Superman: Dawn of Justice‚Äù), Ron Livingston (‚ÄúLoudermilk,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Conjuring‚Äù), Maribel Verd√∫ (‚ÄúElite,‚Äù ‚ÄúY tu mam√° tambi√©n‚Äù), Kiersey Clemons (‚ÄúZack Snyder‚Äôs Justice League,‚Äù ‚ÄúSweetheart‚Äù), Antje Traue (‚ÄúKing of Ravens,‚Äù ‚ÄúMan of Steel‚Äù) and Michael Keaton (‚ÄúSpider-Man: Homecoming,‚Äù ‚ÄúBatman‚Äù).

‚ÄúThe Flash‚Äù is produced by Barbara Muschietti (the ‚ÄúIT‚Äù films, ‚ÄúMama‚Äù) and Michael Disco (‚ÄúRampage,‚Äù ‚ÄúSan Andreas‚Äù). The screenplay is by Christina Hodson (‚ÄúBirds of Prey,‚Äù ‚ÄúBumblebee‚Äù), with a screen story by John Francis Daley & Jonathan Goldstein (‚ÄúDungeons & Dragons: Honor Among Thieves,‚Äù ‚ÄúSpider-Man: Homecoming‚Äù) and Joby Harold (‚ÄúTransformers: Rise of the Beasts,‚Äù ‚ÄúArmy of the Dead‚Äù), based on characters from DC. The executive producers 
are Toby Emmerich, Walter Hamada, Galen Vaisman and Marianne Jenkins.

Joining director Muschietti behind the camera are director of photography Henry Braham (‚ÄúGuardians of the Galaxy Vol. 3,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Suicide Squad‚Äù), production designer Paul Denham Austerberry (‚ÄúIT Chapter Two,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Shape of Water‚Äù), editors Jason Ballantine (the ‚ÄúIT‚Äù films, ‚ÄúThe Great Gatsby‚Äù) and Paul Machliss (‚ÄúThe Gentlemen,‚Äù ‚ÄúBaby Driver‚Äù), and costume designer Alexandra Byrne (‚ÄúDoctor Strange,‚Äù ‚ÄúGuardians of the Galaxy‚Äù); the score is by Benjamin Wallfisch 
(‚ÄúThe Invisible Man,‚Äù the ‚ÄúIT‚Äù films).

Warner Bros. Pictures presents a Double Dream/a Disco Factory production of an Andy Muschietti film, ‚ÄúThe Flash.‚Äù It will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures and is set to open in theaters in North America on June 16, 2023 and internationally beginning 14 June 2023.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3694 - 14 Feb 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3694: Toofan Aa Gaya Hai
--------------------------------------------------------
The mysterious person writes a message on Gokuldham's notice board, and Babita notices someone trespassing, so she immediately yells out of fear. Gokuldham's men want to catch the trespasser or the ghost, but they're scared to face him, so Sodhi leads them. All the men go to the garden and try to find the person who might have sent those mysterious gifts. After a long search, they find no traces of any stranger. While all of them gather at Gokuldham Park, suddenly they hear "Sakharam's" horn beep. So, is this anonymous person up to stealing Bhide's "Sakharam"? Stay tuned!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3694, 14 Feb 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: How these buildings made Turkey-Syria‚Äôs earthquake so deadly
snippet.description:
And can the buildings be fixed?

Subscribe and turn on notifications üîî  so you don't miss any videos: http://goo.gl/0bsAjO 

On the morning of February 6, a pair of powerful earthquakes, 7.8 and 7.6,  hit Turkey and Syria. On top of that, the region was hit with strong aftershocks, which made the destruction even worse. The death toll is already in the tens of thousands with many victims still lying beneath the rubble. 

Multiple factors led to this earthquake being so devastating, like fault lines, neighborhoods still reeling from war and delayed rescue missions. But what made this earthquake particularly catastrophic was unsafe buildings. According to the Turkish government, over 6,000 buildings collapsed because of this earthquake. And that‚Äôs likely because of the way they were built.

This video will explain how bad building design made the Turkey-Syria earthquake more deadly than it had to be. 

Sources and further information: 

This report from Turkish civil engineers helped us understand the impact the Izmit earthquake had on soft story buildings: http://www.bupim.com/yayinlar/bupim-pdf/ECAS66.pdf

localized.title: How these buildings made Turkey-Syria‚Äôs earthquake so deadly
localized.description:
And can the buildings be fixed?

Subscribe and turn on notifications üîî  so you don't miss any videos: http://goo.gl/0bsAjO 

On the morning of February 6, a pair of powerful earthquakes, 7.8 and 7.6,  hit Turkey and Syria. On top of that, the region was hit with strong aftershocks, which made the destruction even worse. The death toll is already in the tens of thousands with many victims still lying beneath the rubble. 

Multiple factors led to this earthquake being so devastating, like fault lines, neighborhoods still reeling from war and delayed rescue missions. But what made this earthquake particularly catastrophic was unsafe buildings. According to the Turkish government, over 6,000 buildings collapsed because of this earthquake. And that‚Äôs likely because of the way they were built.

This video will explain how bad building design made the Turkey-Syria earthquake more deadly than it had to be.

#HiphopTamizha #rnb #hiphop #rap #poipoipoi #musicvideo 

The new song ‚ÄúPoi poi poi‚Äù by Hiphop Tamizha is a fusion of rap and R&b over a catchy beat that has rock vibes  that explores the theme of lies and deceit in relationships. With emotive lyrics and a catchy beat, the song delves into the negative impact of dishonesty on love and trust, and the destruction it can cause.

Farq is the story of two different individuals, Irsa (Sehar Khan) and Kamal (Faysal Quraishi) who come together to form an unusual union under compromising circumstances.

snippet.title: FAST X | Official Hindi Trailer (Universal Studios) - HD
snippet.description:
In cinemas soon

Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/UniversalIND

Director: Louis Leterrier
Writer: Zach Dean
Writer: Dan Mazeau
Producer: Neal H. Moritz
Producer: Vin Diesel
Producer/Writer: Justin Lin
Producer: Jeff Kirschenbaum
Producer: Samantha Vincent
Executive Producer: Joseph M. Caracciolo Jr.
Executive Producer: David Cain
Executive Producer: Chris Morgan
Executive Producer: Amanda Lewis
Executive Producer: Mark Bomback
Cast: Vin Diesel, Michelle Rodriguez, Tyrese Gibson, Chris ‚ÄúLudacris‚Äù Bridges, Jason Momoa, Nathalie Emmanuel, Jordana Brewster, John Cena, Jason Statham, Sung Kang, Alan Ritchson, Daniela Melchior, Scott Eastwood, with Helen Mirren, Charlize Theron, Brie Larson and Rita Moreno

The end of the road begins. 

Fast X, the tenth film in the Fast & Furious Saga, launches the final chapters of one of cinema‚Äôs most storied and popular global franchises, now in its third decade and still going strong with the same core cast and characters as when it began.

Over many missions and against impossible odds, Dom Toretto (Vin Diesel) and his family have outsmarted, out-nerved and outdriven every foe in their path. Now, they confront the most lethal opponent they‚Äôve ever faced: A terrifying threat emerging from the shadows of the past who‚Äôs fueled by blood revenge, and who is determined to shatter this family and destroy everything‚Äîand everyone‚Äîthat Dom loves, forever.  
 
In 2011‚Äôs Fast Five, Dom and his crew took out nefarious Brazilian drug kingpin Hernan Reyes and decapitated his empire on a bridge in Rio De Janeiro. What they didn‚Äôt know was that Reyes‚Äô son, Dante (Aquaman‚Äôs Jason Momoa), witnessed it all and has spent the last 12 years masterminding a plan to make Dom pay the ultimate price. 
 
Dante‚Äôs plot will scatter Dom‚Äôs family from Los Angeles to the catacombs of Rome, from Brazil to London and from Portugal to Antarctica. New allies will be forged and old enemies will resurface. But everything changes when Dom discovers that his own 8-year-old son (Leo Abelo Perry, Black-ish) is the ultimate target of Dante‚Äôs vengeance. 
 
Directed by Louis Leterrier (Clash of the Titans, The Incredible Hulk), Fast X stars returning cast members Michelle Rodriguez, Tyrese Gibson, Chris ‚ÄúLudacris‚Äù Bridges, Nathalie Emmanuel, Jordana Brewster, Sung Kang, Jason Statham, John Cena and Scott Eastwood, with Oscar¬Æ winner Helen Mirren and Oscar¬Æ winner Charlize Theron. 
 
The film also features an extraordinary new cast including Oscar¬Æ winner Brie Larson as Tess, a rogue representative from the Agency; Alan Richtson (Reacher) as Aimes, the new head of the Agency who doesn‚Äôt hold the same fondness for Dom‚Äôs crew as his predecessor, Mr. Nobody; Daniela Melchior (The Suicide Squad) as a Brazilian street racer with a powerful tie to Dom‚Äôs past; and legendary Oscar¬Æ winner Rita Moreno as Dom and Mia‚Äôs Abuelita Toretto. 
 
Fast X is produced by Neal H. Moritz, Vin Diesel, Justin Lin, Jeff Kirschenbaum and Samantha Vincent. The executive producers are Joseph M. Caracciolo, Jr., David Cain, Chris Morgan, Amanda Lewis and Mark Bomback.

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku

Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha

Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.description:
#inmalayalam #anuragtalks #malayalam 

The Indian Ministry of Mines reported the discovery of 5.9 million tonnes of inferred lithium ore on their Twitter on 09/02/2023. This deposit alone makes India the country with the fifth-largest lithium reserves in the world. The deposit, lies in the Reasi district in the provinces of Jammu and Kashmir. Lithium is a non-ferrous metal and is one of the key components in batteries of electric vehicles (EVs).With the EV push from governments the world over, the element has become very crucial in the manufacturing of these vehicles. But is that so easy to make use of it ? In this video i am explaining about the discovery of Lithium in J&K and why it's a big deal for India.

snippet.description:
Presenting you the Official Trailer of #Dhanush in & as #Vaathi! #VaathiTrailer

Vaathi / SIR is an upcoming Tamil/Telugu bilingual film written & directed by Venky Atluri. Music is composed by GV Prakash Kumar & Cinematography is handled by J Yuvraj. Sithara Entertainments headed by Suryadevara Naga Vamsi will be co-producing this film along with Sai Soujanya (Fortune Four Cinemas). The film is Presented by Srikara Studios.

Starring: Dhanush, Samyuktha
Co-Starring: Sai Kumar,Tanikella Bharani,Samuthirakani,Thotapalli Madhu, Narra Srinivas, Pammi Sai, Hyper Aadhi, Shara, Aadukalam Naren, Ilavarasu, Motta Rajendran, Hareesh Peradi, Praveena & Others.

CREW: 
Production Designer: Avinash Kolla
Editor: Navin Nooli
DOP: J Yuvraj
Music: G. V. Prakash Kumar
Action Choreographer - Venkat
Producers: Naga Vamsi S - Sai Soujanya
Written & Directed By: Venky Atluri
Banners: Sithara Entertainments - Fortune Four Cinemas

snippet.title: NEW! Maddam Sir - Ep 737 - 14 Feb 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 737: Shazia Ki Majboori
--------------------------------------------
Shazia is welcomed at Haseen Mallik's home, and Maddam Sir informs her that Pushpa Ji and Karishma Singh will assist her in passing the exams. Shazia inquires Maddam Sir about Indian laws governing women's consent to marriage. She informs Maddam Sir that there are still areas where there are no police stations and girls are forced to marry against their will. Pushpa Ji tries to assist Shazia with her Hindi lessons, which aids her in her investigation of Shazia. Later, the vegetable seller informs Pushpa Ji that some people were looking for a girl who looked like Shazia the night before. Keep an eye out!

Show Name ‚Äì Maddam Sir
Star Cast ‚Äì  Gulki Joshi, Yukti Kapoor, Sonali Naik, Bhavika Sharma, Pankhuri Awasthy Rode, Priyanshu Singh, and Ajay Jadhav
Episode No ‚Äì 737, 14 Feb 2023
Produced By ‚Äì  Jay Mehta

#MaddamSir  #‡§Æ‡•à‡§°‡•ç‡§°‡§Æ‡§∏‡§∞ #SAB

Click here to Subscribe to SAB TV Channel: 
https://www.youtube.com/user/sabtv?sub_confirmation=1

About The Show:
-----------------------------
Set in Lucknow the show is based in one such all-women Police station made by 4 beautiful quirky women. Pushpa, the oldest of them, is the head constable who tries to balance her life between home and work. Karishma, the Sub Inspector, is fish out of the water as she is at loggerheads with the philosophy of the police station. She beats before she talks but now she has to solve all cases through reconciliation. Santosh Sharma is a young new recruit and a typical lonely girl in the city. The head of the pack is S.H.O Haseena Mallik, witty, romantic leads by example. The common challenge for all these women is to bring sensitivity to their policing while dealing with cases that come to this police station. Hence their solution is most unusual. The characters and the circumstances add to the fun and humor of the show. While Pushpa and Karishma are the saas-bahu duo, who keep us entertained by their Squabbles, Haseena - Karishma's ideological differences add to the drama madam and comedy.

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide pays a visit to Hathi bhai's home and accuses his son of pulling the mystery gift prank on him. He tells Hathi bhai that he suspected him because he overheard him talking about a surprise the day before. Komal, Hathi bhai's wife, questions that this prankster may have sent unusual gifts to everyone in Gokuldham, so they decide to check on others. Jetha examines the toy dog for clues about the sender. Everyone later gathers at Gokuldham to share their personal stories about these anonymous gifts.

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.
